keyFacts: The document is a TECS Person Encounter List generated by U.S. Customs and Border Protection on April 6, 2021.
It contains 22 travel records for an individual associated with document number 094332776, spanning from 1997 to 2016.
The travel pattern shows frequent flights between Los Angeles (LAX) and London (LHR/LGW), with carriers including Virgin Atlantic (VS) and British Airways (BA).
The document lists specific CBP (Customs and Border Protection) port codes associated with various airports, including LAX, JFK, Palm Beach, and Teterboro.
No personal identifying information (name, DOB) is visible in the provided text; the records are referenced by a document number.
